Load country-wide data by NACE

Source: R/pv_load_cr.R
pv_cr_monthlypay_nace.Rd

Load country-wide data by NACE (single-letter industry codes)

Usage

pv_cr_monthlypay_nace(path, sheet = 5)

Arguments

path

path to file, filename should be in the form e.g. CR_YYQ_MZS.xlsx".

sheet

Sheet number, defaults to 5

Value

a tibble

Examples

pv_cr_monthlypay_nace(system.file("extdata", "CR_204_MZS.xlsx", package = "ispv"))
